{"tid":2137862,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"做main con真係好撚困身","createTime":"2020-08-03T08:48:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T12:59:53.000Z","uid":35931,"like":75,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"42c7c859feb58b54ea700babe7eb2b6460b7914e","tid":2137862,"uid":35931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T08:48:31.000Z","msg":"做撚左main con 5、6年到啦大約<br />\n細公司仔叫做算一腳踢<br />\n成撚日都要同上家開會<br />\n開完番來又要同d 判頭呀管工夾番咁<br />\n對上家果時就比人屌進度慢<br />\n對判頭管工果時又比人屌出圖慢<br />\n一日收4、50個電話變左好撚平常咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n放假都要聽電話<br />\n你唔聽既第日番到公司都係自己食番哂d屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話就話長短週<br />\n但通常做做下都會變全長週趕進度<br />\n星期日有時都要加班<br />\n<br />\n其實係咪行行都係咁？<br />\n我都係呻下刷下存在感<br />\n打擾哂咁多位<br />\n完"},{"pid":"af3ab44e71f5d21fff493f097659676b5be5ddee","tid":2137862,"uid":169492,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T08:50:06.000Z","msg":"做緊你上家<br />\n對唔住最多今日唔再催你"},{"pid":"e7590460bf982033a8e3f2922c4d64e05ca17f17","tid":2137862,"uid":42674,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T08:52:02.000Z","msg":"行行都係咁"},{"pid":"82daf2982b9471ec35be1f7b25bed116a6d4149c","tid":2137862,"uid":270308,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T08:52:27.000Z","msg":"咁你逗幾多人工先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f49a442348d3e05c78e16be394cc56e019e8c50e","tid":2137862,"uid":283310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T08:52:33.000Z","msg":"做maincon的你，身體如何？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2124069\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2124069</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2fa10df2ec69e2a155626a0089ef1b7755465b3e","tid":2137862,"uid":192409,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-